{"tid":2209122,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"媽的貢丸，頭先翻工被娛樂台某知名會員搶撚咗把傘……","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T19:02:49.000Z","uid":152123,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ed72d3848aec3ca4118d286d50d4243af6a4d958","tid":2209122,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"頭先翻M記抹緊檯一邊上連登<br />\n有個著到夏威夷風情咁嘅人 行埋嚟見到我user name<br />\n就撻朵話自己係娛樂台某知名會員(有畀手機我睇證明)<br />\n就要脅我話會放我上連登<br />\n我求牠唔好咁做 佢就叫我借把傘畀佢<br />\n結果我屈服咗&hellip;佢臨走前仲話今晚終於有嘢打小強&hellip;佢老母吖&hellip;<br />\n大家出街上連登真係要小心啲&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec7fd606e6fbf18d32cb263b10ce510bbaf1b68","tid":2209122,"uid":203454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:51:16.000Z","msg":"連隻狗都驚<br />\nChing你會唔會廢咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a7e89b0ea1badd24a3ca137566c9ce371e469e","tid":2209122,"uid":117802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ec7fd606e6fbf18d32cb263b10ce510bbaf1b68","tid":2209122,"uid":203454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:51:16.000Z","msg":"連隻狗都驚<br />\nChing你會唔會廢咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:51:38.000Z","msg":"你搶人遮？"},{"pid":"7f3814ad25b88a8ab3b43e9814ff56a9084dfeb3","tid":2209122,"uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />私了佢啦 仲等咩"},{"pid":"a74a96c28361d3c66b98a41b616ad3e1fc3a5271","tid":2209122,"uid":203454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3a7e89b0ea1badd24a3ca137566c9ce371e469e","tid":2209122,"uid":117802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"qu